{"word":"ταρ","slug":"ταρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n102408\" key=\"tar\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ταρ</orth>, acc. to Hdn.Gr.<bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Oxy.:2:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.22</biblScope> </bibl> an enclit. Conjunction (<sense id=\"n102408.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">παραπληρωματικὸς σύνδεσμος</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Trypho\">Trypho</a></author> </bibl> </cit> in Kenyon <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">Class. Texts</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.116</biblScope> </bibl>), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἴ ταρ, οὔ ταρ</foreign>, to be read in place of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἴτ᾽ ἄρ᾽, οὔτ᾽ ἄρ᾽</foreign>, as in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:65\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.65</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:93\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">93</biblScope> </bibl>; there is Ms. authority for <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ταρ</itype> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.8</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:761\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.761</biblScope> </bibl>; in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:182\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.182</biblScope> </bibl> one of the editions of <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author> </bibl> had <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ταρ</itype>, the other <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">γαρ</itype>, and codd. are divided: Cobet conjectured <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ταρ</itype> for <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">γαρ</itype>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:61\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.61</biblScope> </bibl> (where his cj. is now confirmed by two codd.), and in other places, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Misc.Crit.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">315</biblScope> </bibl>:—on the relation between <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὖταρ, αὖ</foreign>, and <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ταρ</itype>, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg003:254:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.D.\">A.D.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Conj.\">Conj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">254.2</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}